因为他们在特朗普的椭圆形办公室里游行的儿子</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
 Spike Lee回应Kendrick Lamar的超级碗致敬https://www.nme.com/news/film/spike-lee-responds-to-kendrick-lamars-super-bowl-tribute-3837420?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=spike-lee-responds-to-kendrick-拉马尔式鲍龙 - 分秀Victoria LuxfordWed, 12 Feb 2025 15:42:19 +0000 Film NewsMusic NewsNewsOscars https://www.nme.com/?p=3837420 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Spike-Lee-and-Kendrick-Lamar.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="肯德里克·拉马尔（Kendrick Lamar）" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Spike-Lee-and-Kendrick-Lamar.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Spike-Lee-and-Kendrick-Lamar-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Spike-Lee-and-Kendrick-Lamar-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Spike-Lee-and-Kendrick-Lamar-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Spike-Lee-and-Kendrick-Lamar-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Spike-Lee-and-Kendrick-Lamar-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>塞缪尔·杰克逊（Samuel L Jackson）在节目中的角色回荡了导演的一部电影</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/spike-lee-responds-to-kendrick-lamars-super-bowl-tribute-3837420">Spike Lee对Kendrick Lamar的超级碗致敬作出回应，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Spike-Lee-and-Kendrick-Lamar.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="肯德里克·拉马尔（Kendrick Lamar）" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Spike-Lee-and-Kendrick-Lamar.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Spike-Lee-and-Kendrick-Lamar-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Spike-Lee-and-Kendrick-Lamar-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Spike-Lee-and-Kendrick-Lamar-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Spike-Lee-and-Kendrick-Lamar-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Spike-Lee-and-Kendrick-Lamar-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/spike-lee">斯派克·李（Spike Lee）</a>感谢肯德里克<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kendrick-lamar">·拉马尔（Kendrick Lamar）</a>在纪录的2025年超级碗半场表演中提到了他的作品。说唱歌手演员<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/samuel-l-jackson">塞缪尔·L·杰克逊（Samuel L Jackson）</a>的角色与李的一部电影类似，并参考了李的<em>40英亩土地和一家Mule</em>制作公司。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：</strong> <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/drake-and-kendrick-lamars-feud-the-full-timeline-3754820">Drake和Kendrick Lamar的仇恨 - 完整的时间表</a></li></ul><p>在演出期间，杰克逊扮演了节目每个部分的叙述者山姆大叔的角色。电影爱好者注意到角色与多莱梅德的角色之间的相似之处，叙述者角色杰克逊（Jackson）在李（Lee）的2015年电影《奇拉克》 <em>（Chi-Raq）</em>中扮演。这位电影制片人去社交媒体上赞美他的电影和制片公司的参考。</p><p> Lee在Instagram上发布了一段有关该表演的视频，并带有标题：“我要感谢我的兄弟肯德里克（Kendrick）的40英亩和一个mule喊声，这是自NYU Grad Film School以来我制作公司的名字。我想向我的莫尔豪斯（Morehouse）兄弟塞缪尔·杰克逊（Samuel Jackson）发出特别的喊叫声，塞缪尔·杰克逊（Samuel Jackson）以山姆叔叔的身份开始了这个超级碗半场盛会，您可能已经把他当作Chi-Raq的Dolemedes。”</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/oscars">奥斯卡奖</a>得主继续说：“在内战之后，40英亩和m子是对前被奴役的非裔美国人进行赔偿的提议。该提案旨在提供土地和资源，以提供土地和资源，以帮助人们实现经济独立性。这个诺言最终被打破了。快乐黑色的主角”。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DF6sTQ9xCLp/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;