, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Backstreet-Boys.-Credit-Brian-Ziff-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Backstreet-Boys.-Credit-Brian-Ziff-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Backstreet-Boys.-Credit-Brian-Ziff-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Backstreet-Boys.-Credit-Brian-Ziff-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="/artists/Backstreet-Boys">后街的男孩</a>宣布了他们的“进入千年”的拉斯维加斯球体居留权，该居住将于今年夏天晚些时候开始。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/blogs/nme-blogs/backstreet-boys-interview-2018-2316121">“我们是流行音乐的滚石乐队”：后街男孩在音乐中谈论25年</a></strong></li></ul><p>由AJ McLean，Howie Dorough，Nick Carter，Kevin Richardson和Brian Littrell组成的标志性Boyband将于7月11日接管拉斯维加斯的最先进的娱乐场所，直到27日至27日。</p><p>由Live Nation制作的Backstreet Boys“进入千年”的居留权将看到五重奏表演“我想要的那样”和“比生命更大”等热门歌曲，这将通过尖端的视觉和声音来增强由Sphere的革命性沉浸式技术实现。</p><p>他们的居住也将使他们成为第一个扮演球体的流行表演。 </p><figure id="attachment_3837414" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3837414" style="width: 1500px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3837414" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Backstreet-Boys-Las-Vegas-Sphere-residency-tour-poster.-Credit-PRESS.jpg" alt="后街男孩拉斯维加斯球体居住之旅海报。信用：出版" width="1500" height="1950" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Backstreet-Boys-Las-Vegas-Sphere-residency-tour-poster.-Credit-PRESS.jpg 1500w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Backstreet-Boys-Las-Vegas-Sphere-residency-tour-poster.-Credit-PRESS-400x520.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Backstreet-Boys-Las-Vegas-Sphere-residency-tour-poster.-Credit-PRESS-800x1040.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Backstreet-Boys-Las-Vegas-Sphere-residency-tour-poster.-Credit-PRESS-696x905.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Backstreet-Boys-Las-Vegas-Sphere-residency-tour-poster.-