ull size-full wp-post-image" alt="Alabama Barker and Danielle Bregoli aka Bhad Bhabie. Photo credit: Presley Ann/Getty Images for Spotify; Paul Archuleta/FilmMagic" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/alabama-barker-danielle-bregoli-2000-x-1270-.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/alabama-barker-danielle-bregoli-2000-x-1270--400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/alabama-barker-danielle-bregoli-2000-x-1270--800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/alabama-barker-danielle-bregoli-2000-x-1270--696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/alabama-barker-danielle-bregoli-2000-x-1270--1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/alabama-barker-danielle-bregoli-2000-x-1270--1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="/artists/alabama-barker">Alabama Barker</a> has clapped back at <a href="/artists/bhad-bhabie">Bhad Bhabie</a> on her new song &#39;Cry Bhabie&#39; – shutting down claims she was involved with Bhabie&#39;s baby&#39;s father, Le Vaughn.</p><p> Earlier this year, Bhabie (real name Danielle Bregoli) went on a tirade, accusing Barker of trying to steal Le Vaughn from her – which the 19-year-old continues to deny. Subsequently, Bregoli released <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fK-eXPMOR1E" target="_blank" rel="noopener">&#39;Over Cooked&#39;</a> – in which she insinuated that Alabama had <em>“fucked and got pregnant”</em> by two people, later confirming that <a href="https://www.youtube.com/shorts/--AlwzN4lW0" target="_blank" rel="noopener">she was referring to Soulja Boy and Tyga in an Instagram livestream</a> .</p><p> Over the weekend, Alabama dropped the music video to &#39;Cry Bhabie&#39;, her reply to &#39;Over Cooked&#39; where she set the record straight on the whole ordeal. First, Barker revealed that her dad – <a href="/artists/travis-barker">Travis Barker</a> of <a href="/artists/blink-182">Blink 182</a> – encouraged her to respond, rapping: <em>“Yeah, my life a movie, daddy Spike Lee /</em> <em>Travis told me, &#39;Go on and turn up&#39;.”</em> </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Alabama Barker - Cry Bhabie (Official Video)" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/y1M8Ea46MgU?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> Then, she proceeded to explain her side of the story – stating that Vaughn was the one to initiate a relationship, claiming that he <em>“tried to pipe”</em> her on a recent Las Vegas trip with their mutual friends. Barker said she rejected him and, to this day, he still tries to contact her despite Bregoli&#39;s public disdain for her.</p><p> She also addressed Bhabie&#39;s claims that she slept and was impregnated by rapper <a href="/artists/tyga">Tyga</a> in &#39;Over Cooked&#39;. Barker name-checked the &#39;Taste&#39; rapper before alluding that the &#39;Cash Me Outside&#39; star was on pills when she made the claim: <em>“The pills got you higher / Turned you to a liar / You must be TMZ / Bitch, don&#39;t make me call a Tyga.”</em></p><p> She later poked fun at the claim, rapping: <em>“Like, what&#39;s the tea? / Lied about some pregnancy / Just wanna be in my family tree”.</em></p><p> In retaliation, Alabama fired back her own allegations at Bhabie, alleging that Vaughn has been sleeping with Bregoli&#39;s best friend. She mocked Bhabie for continuing her relationship with Vaughn despite all the cheating allegations against him: <em>“And the sad part about it / You still gon&#39; bring him home.”</em></p><p> Recently, Bhabie shared a snippet on Instagram of her second diss track aimed at Barker, &#39;Damn Alabama&#39;. In the clip, she said she is Alabama&#39;s <em>“OG”</em> – adding: <em>“How the fuck can I be a fan of a bitch I raised?”</em> Bregoli also directly responded to Barker&#39;s claims that Vaughn cheated on Bhabie with her best friend, revealing she and her friend Tilan “ <em>fucked him together”</em> – clearing Vaughn of that allegation.</p><p> Alabama&#39;s mother Shanna Moakler has since <a href="https://www.instagram.com/reel/DFyXmVZRoSA/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">defended her daughter in a new Instagram video</a> , lip-syncing: “I <em>&#39;m just telling you that my daughter is not a fighter. My daughter&#39;s not a fighter, but I am. Tell your daughter to leave my daughter alone</em> .” In the caption, she tagged Barker and wrote, “Don&#39;t mess with my Bama!”</p><p> Earlier this month, Soulja Boy threatened to sue Bregoli for saying he slept with Alabama in one of his infamous Instagram Live rants. “So you mean to tell me because I ain&#39;t let you suck my dick, you mad?,” he said. “You get on this internet lying on my name?”</p><p> Tyga and Alabama also responded to Bhabie&#39;s allegation. The former tweeted: “This the dumbest shit I ever heard. Y&#39;all believe anything y&#39;all see online. I have never had any sort of physical relationship with Alabama. It&#39;s honestly ridiculous I even have to address it.” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Over Cooked" width="696" height="522" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/fK-eXPMOR1E?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> Barker initially <a href="https://www.instagram.com/theshaderoom/p/DFdCwryOQsl/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">posted a long statement on her Instagram story</a> , making it clear that she had “never been pregnant, never had an abortion, and have never been alone with Tyga or Soulja Boy.”</p><p> She continued: “The idea of any personal relationship between us is completely fabricated – nothing more than a sad baseless attempt to gain attention. I won&#39;t continue to entertain this nonsense, but this will be the last time I address pathetic lies.”</p><p> In other news, Bregoli revealed that <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bhad-bhabie-reveals-cancer-diagnosis-reportedly-seeking-treatment-3811336">she was diagnosed with cancer</a> last November. There has been no confirmation as to what type of cancer she has.</p><p> The post <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/alabama-barker-hits-back-at-bhad-bhabie-on-new-track-cry-bhabie-tyga-3836553">Alabama Barker drops diss track &#39;Cry Bhabie&#39; – Bhad Bhabie teases her reply</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
